## Detection

### Check Dampened Routes
```bash
show ip bgp dampened-paths
```

---

### View BGP Routes
```bash
show ip bgp
```

Look for:
```text
Damped Routes
```

---

## Configuration Example

### Enable Damping
```bash
bgp dampening
```

---

### Custom Parameters
```bash
bgp dampening 15 750 2000 60
```

